body:
@GeoffreyBooth in merging the latest `ast` into my branch and updating the Prettier plugin to use that dependency, I found that the AST structure being generated for JSX empty expressions (`{}`) was incorrect

Instead of a `JSXEmptyExpression` node *replacing* the typical `JSXExpressionContainer` node, it actually needs to be *nested inside* a `JSXExpressionContainer` node

So this PR updates the AST generated for JSX empty expressions to correctly match Babel AST

