But I think the bigger problem is that [this](https://babeljs.io/repl/#?babili=false&browsers=&build=&builtIns=false&code_lz=G4QwTgBGCmB2Am1IF4IAoCUFkD4IG8AoCCAHhB1IHoLiyAjSqxwgX0KA&debug=false&forceAllTransforms=false&shippedProposals=false&circleciRepo=&evaluate=true&fileSize=false&lineWrap=false&presets=react%2Cenv&prettier=false&targets=&version=6.26.0&envVersion=1.6.2):
